<note n="0878003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0878003">備＝被【明】</note>
<note n="0878004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0878004">一切…十五 Trayodaśamaḥ(pañca-daśamaḥ?)sarva-karma-triyārthaḥ.paṭala-visaraḥ.</note>
<note n="0878005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0878005">〔之一〕－【宋】【明】</note>
<note n="0879001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0879001">寶座印 Bhadra-pīṭha.</note>
<note n="0879002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0879002">Namaḥ samanta-buddhā ām ap atihataśāsanānām, tadyathā Oṁ kumāra-rūpiṇa darśaya darśayamātmano bhūti samud bhāvaya svapnaṁ me niveda yathā-bhūtam, hūṁ hūṁ phaṭ phaṭ svāhā.</note>
<note n="0879003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0879003">縛＝嚩【宋】【明】</note>
<note n="0879004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0879004">〔引〕－【明】</note>
<note n="0879005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0879005">粆＝砂【明】</note>
<note n="0879006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0879006">Padma-rāga.</note>
<note n="0880001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0880001">Namaḥ samanta-buddhānām apratihata śāsanānām, tadyathā he he mahā-krodha ṣaṇmukha, ṣaṭcaraṇa, sarva-vighna-ghātaya, hūṁ hūṁ, kiṁ cirāyasi vināyaka jīvitānta-kara, duḥ svapnaṁ me nāśaya, laṅgha laṅgha samaya-manusmara phaṭ phaṭ svāhā.</note>
<note n="0880002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0880002">阿＝何【明】</note>
</p>
